nosuid cannot be set on the mount point from which the binary is executed,
because this prevents capabilities from working. Unfortunately, this seems
to mean that encrypted home partition from ubuntu cannot be used. 

note: use ram disk for pivot_root so it is more dynamic 

ensure all snprintfs are checking for truncation and negative returns 


need  libxrandr-dev

apt-get install libcap-dev

CAP_IPC_LOCK + CAP_SYS_ADMIN
